  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced", 
    "date": "1981-02-03", 
    "text": "Declares the sense of Congress that the President shall take steps to: (1) call upon the Soviet Union to permit the resurrection of the Ukrainian churches of various Jewish and Christian denominations; (2) contact the officials of the Soviet Union to secure freedom of worship in the Soviet Union and Eastern Europe; and (3) raise in the United Nations the question of Stalin's liquidation of such churches."
